{
  "stem": "23737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we were eventuality put on the train-- by then it wasn't wagons, we were put on a train-- to go back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we traveled a good few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I arrived in the main station in Budapest and get off the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And who is standing at the platform but my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the war ended, she went every single day to the Jewish offices where they had, where they got all the news from the various camps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And through that friend of mine who brought the name of a lot of people, whom he knew who were in Theresien, she got to know that I was alive.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from that day on, she came every single day to the station to wait for the train to come.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "End of June.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The last few days of June, I think arrived about the 30th of June.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, and she was standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was a moment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They have been taken from that ghetto house as well to the same area where my husband's family was under Wallenberg's auspices.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they survived there-- my mother and my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when that, when the war was over, they went back to our old flat where  we used to live, what was by then given to a non-Jewish family who, who were bombed out from their flat.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "An elderly father and his widowed daughter were living in our flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when my mother came back, they were moved into one room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they left us the other rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
